OL,3,CManhunt for predator convicted of
OL,4,Cabusing teenage girls
OL,6,FPolice have launched a manhunt for a
OL,7,Fpredator who is on the run after being
OL,8,Fconvicted of sex offences against
OL,9,Fteenage girls.
OL,11,FSharam Muhamadi, 21, was one of two
OL,12,Fmen found guilty of abusing girls as
OL,13,Fyoung as 12 following a trial at
OL,14,FSheffield Crown Court.
OL,16,FHe failed to appear for his trial
OL,17,Fafter being granted bail by the court.
OL,19,FIt is believed Muhamadi, of Hexthorpe
OL,20,FRoad, Doncaster, travelled to
OL,21,FBirmingham between 16 and 18 May.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
