OL,3,CManhunt for predator convicted of
OL,4,Cabusing teenage girls
OL,6,FThe last confirmed sighting was in
OL,7,FBirmingham city centre on 18 May.
OL,9,FAssistant chief constable Hayley
OL,10,FBarnett, of South Yorkshire Police,
OL,11,Fsaid: "We are wholly focussed on
OL,12,Ffinding Muhamadi and ensuring his
OL,13,Ffaces the consequences of his actions.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781118693
OL,3,CManhunt for predator convicted of
OL,4,Cabusing teenage girls
OL,6,F"Officers have been relentlessly
OL,7,Fpursing all lines of enquiries. We are
OL,8,Fkeeping an open mind of his
OL,9,Fwhereabouts. We believe he is still in
OL,10,Fthe country, but if he is found
OL,11,Fabroad, we will seek the government's
OL,12,Fhelp in doing everything we can to
OL,13,Fextradite him.
OL,15,F"We will not stop until we find him,
OL,16,Fand we will ensure these young girls
OL,17,Fget the justice they deserve."
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
