PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781118693
OL,3,CManhunt for predator convicted of
OL,4,Cabusing teenage girls
OL,6,FMuhamadi's accomplice Bawan Hawre, 28,
OL,7,Fdid stand trial and was found guilty
OL,8,Fof of sexual offences against seven
OL,9,Fteenage girls.
OL,11,FThe court heard an investigation by
OL,12,FSouth Yorkshire Police began in August
OL,13,F2024, when one of the victims, who was
OL,14,Freported missing from home, told
OL,15,Fauthorities she was being exploited.
OL,17,FSix other victims, aged between 12 and
OL,18,F16 years-old, were also identified.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
