FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781118693
OL,3,CManhunt for predator convicted of
OL,4,Cabusing teenage girls
OL,6,FThe jury heard Hawre and Muahamdi used
OL,7,Ffake names to contact girls via social
OL,8,Fmedia, offering them vapes, e-
OL,9,Fcigarettes and money.
OL,11,FAfter arranging to meet them in person
OL,12,Fthey would give them alcohol and drugs
OL,13,Fin order to abuse them. The jury heard
OL,14,Fthe girls were transported between
OL,15,FBarnsley and Doncaster to be exploited.
OL,17,FHawre, formerly of Hexthorpe Road,
OL,18,FDoncaster, was convicted of six counts
OL,19,Fof trafficking, six counts of rape, as
OL,20,Fwell as grooming and false
OL,21,Fimprisonment.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
