PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781118693
OL,3,CManhunt for predator convicted of
OL,4,Cabusing teenage girls
OL,6,FMuhamadi was convicted in his absence
OL,7,Fof two counts of trafficking girls for
OL,8,Fexploitation.
OL,10,FBoth men will be sentenced on 11 June.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/6
